  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_1",
    "text": "FAMILY Harry, Holly, Emma and Steve",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05084492298489607,
      0.17166372721928277,
      0.22072678331090176,
      0.18106995884773663
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_2",
    "text": "EXCLUSIVE BY MATTHEW BARBOUR",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.04546134290414237,
      0.18718400940623162,
      0.1585165245999701,
      0.21540270429159317
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_3",
    "text": "t the age of four, while her little pals were running about, aughing mehe",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04725586959772693,
      0.21916519694297473,
      0.19979063855241513,
      0.2883009994121105
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_4",
    "text": "Another childhood memory is of Sunday afternoons, when other mums and dads were out for a stroll after lunch and her parents, Pat and Pip, would be holding a seance to commune with the other side.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.047854045162255124,
      0.2887713109935332,
      0.16031105129355466,
      0.38612580834803056
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_5",
    "text": "Emma, 48, now a full-1 time witch, says: \"It seemed normal for me to see – and play with – dead people from the age of just four.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04845222072678331,
      0.38753674309229863,
      0.1686855091969493,
      0.44585537918871254
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_6",
    "text": "\"My first time was at Hampton Court, but ever since then, it's happened regularly. My younger brother Ben and I knew our parents were different, but then, aren't everyon",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.047854045162255124,
      0.44632569077013523,
      0.16210557798713923,
      0.5239271017048794
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_7",
    "text": "She says she inherited her mum's magical powers and \"came out of the closet – the broom closet\" after her parents died from cancer in 2019 and 2020.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04845222072678331,
      0.5248677248677248,
      0.21474502766561987,
      0.5737801293356849
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_8",
    "text": "Sh says: \"I'm the real-life Molly Weasley. Everyone calls me that.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.047854045162255124,
      0.5836566725455614,
      0.20577239419769702,
      0.6527924750146973
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_9",
    "text": "But, unlike the Harry Potter witch, she is a thoroughly modern Molly, with 96,000 followers on Insta- gram and 40,000 on TikTok.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04845222072678331,
      0.6532627865961199,
      0.1579183490354419,
      0.7214579659024103
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_10",
    "text": "And she recently cast her spell on 262 would-be magic makers from across the world, initiating them as witches in on big, free Zoom session.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04845222072678331,
      0.7223985890652558,
      0.16150740242261102,
      0.7905937683715462
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_17",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.27994616419919244,
      0.7807172251616696,
      0.4097502617018095,
      0.8470311581422693
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_27",
    "text": "has always been open with her kids about being a witch. She says: \"They were attracted to the spirituality of it.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7806191117092867,
      0.7896531452087008,
      0.9540900254224615,
      0.8197530864197531
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_22",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.41573201734709136,
      0.7910640799529688,
      0.588604755495738,
      0.830570252792475
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_24",
    "text": "Talking of the Zoom witch initiation, which included women from as far away as Finland and Australia, she says: \"I guided them through the ceremony, helping them become witches, telling them to spread 福 the word far and wide.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5969792133991326,
      0.7910640799529688,
      0.7716464782413638,
      0.8597295708406819
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_13",
    "text": "Emma did not discover her mum was a witch until she was 17, when she rushed home in tears after visiting a psychic fair with Steve, now her husband.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04845222072678331,
      0.7915343915343915,
      0.1627037535516674,
      0.8597295708406819
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_12",
    "text": "6",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1800508449229849,
      0.7915343915343915,
      0.2069687453267534,
      0.8098765432098766
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_16",
    "text": "It seemed normal to me to see dead people",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.17347091371317483,
      0.8117577895355673,
      0.26499177508598776,
      0.8865373309817755
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_28",
    "text": "Her husband is also on \"team witch\", says Emma, whose website has attracted clients wanting help with everything from mental health to fertility issues.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7800209361447585,
      0.8202233980011758,
      0.9552863765515178,
      0.8681951793062904
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_23",
    "text": "Emma says: \"When I tel people I'm a witch, the majority are fascinated and love hearing about what I do, from helping people find happi- ness to healing e,even helping them conseive ef 25 years 心 ago.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.414535666218035,
      0.8300999412110524,
      0.5419470614625392,
      0.9613168724279836
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_19",
    "text": "daughter Holly, then son Harry three years later.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2841333931508898,
      0.8507936507936508,
      0.4055630327501122,
      0.8799529688418577
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_14",
    "text": "A tarot reader had told her she and Steve, then also 17 and an art student like her, would never have children.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0490503962913115,
      0.8606701940035273,
      0.1627037535516674,
      0.9091122868900646
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_25",
    "text": "She has faced hostility from people saying she will \"go to hell for working for the devil\", but Emma says being a witch is \"posi- tive and nat- ural\".And she",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6879018992074174,
      0.86114050558495,
      0.772244653805892,
      0.9584950029394473
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_26",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6137281292059219,
      0.8616108171663727,
      0.6843128458202482,
      0.9547325102880658
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_29",
    "text": "She says: \"I intend to keep spreading the word. Those muggles (people without magical talents) are really missing out\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.781815462838343,
      0.8686654908877132,
      0.9546882009869897,
      0.9081716637272192
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_20",
    "text": "Soon after, moving from London to Cornwall to be closer to nature, Emma began giving clients spiritual guidance, while working in jobs ranging from fashion design to illustration. She became a full-time witch around five years ago and initiated nursery manager Holly as a sea witch in 2021, making a third generation of witches in her family.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2841333931508898,
      0.8808935920047031,
      0.40496485718558395,
      0.9199294532627866
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_18",
    "text": "EMMA GRIFFIN WITCH ONPARANORMAL POWER",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
