      0.9540900254224615,
      0.9373309817754262
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 29
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_15",
    "text": "Determined to help, her mum confessed she was actually a sorceress and would teach Emma thesills tope he reaer In 1999, Emma and Steve had",
